{
  "id": "adv_event_2603_01_03",
  "title": "長瀬麻奈と\nお姉ちゃん",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-evening",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.163398698
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_03-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "あら、この公園に麻奈様とよく来ていたんですの？\n私にとっても馴染み深い場所ですわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 9.315940666200001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-evening",
      "startTime": 6.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_03-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "うん、練習に疲れたら一旦ピアノのことは忘れて\n二人でかくれんぼして遊んでたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.4226067226,
      "endTime": 17.3095002811,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-evening",
      "startTime": 17.5161669096
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_03-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "私がお姉ちゃんを見つけられなくて泣きそうになると\nいつも心配して出てきてくれてたっけ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.5161669096,
      "endTime": 24.104783567,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_03-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "それでも私が泣いちゃった時はコンビニでお菓子を\n買ってきてくれて、ここで一緒に食べていたわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.3114501955,
      "endTime": 32.0419716837,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-evening",
      "startTime": 32.2486383123
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_03-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "ぐぬぬ……妹ですし当然なんですけれど、続々と\n私も知らない幼少期の麻奈様のお話が出てきますわねぇ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.2486383123,
      "endTime": 43.9490689917,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-evening",
      "startTime": 44.1557356201
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_03-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "ですがアイドルとしての麻奈様のことでしたら\n琴乃には負けませんわよ！　次は私のターンですわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.1557356201,
      "endTime": 53.3266195618,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-evening",
      "startTime": 53.5332861904
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_03-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈様はライブが終わると{user}さんに\nニコニコアイスを買ってもらっていたそうでして",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.5332861904,
      "endTime": 60.004261112600005,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_03-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "アイスで乾杯して、二人で海を眺めながら\n勝利を分かち合ったとラジオで言っていましたわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.2109285041,
      "endTime": 67.4153536484,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-evening",
      "startTime": 67.6220202768
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_03-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃん、アイドルになった後もここに来てたんだ\n私と遊んだことも覚えてくれてたのかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.6220202768,
      "endTime": 77.1380971278,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-evening",
      "startTime": 77.3447637563
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_03-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ、きっと。確か琴乃が着けているそのペンダントは\n琴乃が麻奈様にあげた物ですわよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.3447637563,
      "endTime": 85.5631084447,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-evening",
      "startTime": 85.7364391968
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_03-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "うん。お姉ちゃんのお誕生日プレゼントに\n私とお揃いのビーズのネックレスを作って渡したの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.7364391968,
      "endTime": 93.1173460648,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-evening",
      "startTime": 93.3240126933
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_03-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "でも、旅行先で私は自分のをなくしちゃって……\n探しても探しても見つからなかったの。そしたらね――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.3240126933,
      "endTime": 103.7849194851,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_emb-03.m4a",
      "text": "私にくれたネックレス、とっても長かったでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.9543307943,
      "endTime": 110.01199567779999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_glad-07.m4a",
      "text": "解いたら二本になるかな～って思って！　はい、どうぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.0119956778,
      "endTime": 114.7182456977,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3409.0017830999955
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5742.335116500001
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_03-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "……ありがとう、あれ？\nこのネックレス、星型のペンダントも付いてる……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.9249123262,
      "endTime": 125.1818052934,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そう！　お土産屋さんで琴乃が見ていた星のペンダント",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.3884719219,
      "endTime": 129.8884719422,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_laughter-04.m4a",
      "text": "私も素敵だな～って思ったから着けてみたんだ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.8884719422,
      "endTime": 134.1484719601,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ちょっと短くなっちゃったし、元通りではないけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.3551385886,
      "endTime": 138.4088886069,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "形は変わっても琴乃とお揃いなことは変わらないでしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.4088886069,
      "endTime": 143.11513862680002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-evening",
      "startTime": 144.2884790427
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_03-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "アンサーソングを作る時、このペンダントを着けている\nのはお姉ちゃんを近くに感じて勇気をもらえるからなの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.28848006,
      "endTime": 153.95514876130002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-evening",
      "startTime": 154.1618153897
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_03-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃が麻奈様にあげて、麻奈様がまた琴乃にあげた物\n世界に二つしかない、お揃いのペンダントでしたのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.1618153897,
      "endTime": 164.2369170515,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_03-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "落ち込んだ時は、そのペンダントを見ていると\n麻奈様も雑誌のインタビューでおっしゃっていましたわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.44358368,
      "endTime": 171.8919281969,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-evening",
      "startTime": 172.0985948254
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_03-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、きっと琴乃と同じように、お揃いの物を見て\n大切な妹を近くに感じて、元気をもらっていたんですわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 172.0985948254,
      "endTime": 182.8158912351,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-evening",
      "startTime": 183.0225578635
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_03-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "私、お姉ちゃんの落ち込んでる姿を見たことがないの\n絶対に家族の前では暗い顔なんてしなかったから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 183.0225578635,
      "endTime": 192.7247118324,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_03-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "すずの話を聞いて、私はアイドルとしてのお姉ちゃんの\nことを、まだまだ全然知らないんだなって思ったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 192.7150753026,
      "endTime": 200.465138341,
