      "text": "そっか、お姉ちゃん、遙子さんとも来ていたんですね\nこのカレー屋さんは、家族でよく来ていた場所なんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 380.9180397687,
      "endTime": 391.0672238051,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_03-ktn022.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃんとの思い出の場所で\nみんなでご飯を食べながらお話しがしたいと思いまして",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 391.2738904335,
      "endTime": 397.5913054802,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 397.7979721088
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_03-ktn023.m4a",
      "text": "改めて、私の知らない\nアイドル長瀬麻奈の話を聞かせて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 397.7979721088,
      "endTime": 403.7628476163,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 404.1028760612
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_03-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "そうね、琴乃ちゃんが知らない麻奈ちゃん……\n実は、割とよく落ち込んでいた話、とか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 404.1028760612,
      "endTime": 414.7141458214,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 410.3763414083
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_03-suz012.m4a",
      "text": "一体どんなことで！？　これは私も知らない、ラジオや\n雑誌でも語られていないレアなお話の予感……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 414.7666679383,
      "endTime": 424.1075744331,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 414.9028760612
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 424.3142410615
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
