      "text": "いろいろあるけれど、印象的だったのはクイズ番組で\n優勝を逃して一人反省会をしていた時かしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 424.3142410615,
      "endTime": 433.8078235963,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_03-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "へぇ、あの麻奈が……ちょっとやそっとじゃ\n落ち込まなさそうなのに、相当難しいクイズだったのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 434.0142410615,
      "endTime": 442.5620638231,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
